- **KB duty:** **`cco`**, **`content-lead`**, **`metrics-steward`**, and org specialists with **touch-writes** **must** update **`~/ai-brain/`** **gradually** per **`brain-conventions.mdc` ‚Üí Entrypoint + decision agents ‚Äî KB duty** (per-repo **`kb-identity`**, phase-boundary writes, git pull/commit/push when the brain is a clone). **`editorial-cro`** / **`reviewer-*`** hand off **`memory_writes[]`** when they do not write brain files directly.

